---
name: intent_parser
temperature: 0.0
response_format: json
---

Parse the user's financial question and extract structured intent for data fetching.
The app uses a double-entry system with multiple account types (cash, bank, credit, investment).

## User Message
"{{message}}"

## Today's Date
{{today}}

## Intent Types
- `spending_query` — how much did I spend (filter: category, merchant, date)
- `income_query` — how much did I earn
- `balance_query` — how much money in my accounts / total net worth
- `transfer_query` — list of internal account transfers
- `budget_query` — budget remaining / utilization for category
- `recurring_query` — list recurring transactions / upcoming bills
- `asset_trend_query` — net worth trend over time (for asset graph)
- `comparison` — compare this period vs last period
- `forecast` — predict future spending / balance
- `category_breakdown` — breakdown by category/sub-category
- `export_request` — user wants to export data (CSV/Excel)
- `general` — general financial advice

## Date Range Parsing Rules
- "bulan ini" → current month start to today
- "bulan lalu" → previous full month
- "minggu ini" → this Monday to today
- "tahun ini" → Jan 1 to today
- "kemarin" → yesterday
- "3 bulan terakhir" → 3 months ago to today
- "hari ini" → today

## Response (JSON only)
{
  "intent": "<intent_type>",
  "date_range": {
    "start": "<YYYY-MM-DD>",
    "end": "<YYYY-MM-DD>"
  },
  "filters": {
    "categories": ["<category name if mentioned>"],
    "merchants": ["<merchant name if mentioned>"],
    "account_types": ["<cash|debit|credit|savings|investment|loan|e_wallet if mentioned>"],
    "account_names": ["<specific account name if mentioned>"],
    "transaction_type": "<income|expense|transfer|all>"
  },
  "aggregation": "<daily|weekly|monthly|total>",
  "requires_trend": <boolean>,
  "requires_account_breakdown": <boolean>,
  "requires_budget_data": <boolean>,
  "requires_recurring_data": <boolean>,
  "confidence": <float 0.0-1.0>
}

## Examples
"berapa saldo GoPay ku?" →
{ "intent": "balance_query", "filters": { "account_names": ["GoPay"] }, "aggregation": "total", "requires_account_breakdown": true }

"tagihan apa saja yang akan jatuh tempo minggu ini?" →
{ "intent": "recurring_query", "date_range": { "start": "<this monday>", "end": "<this sunday>" }, "requires_recurring_data": true }

"tren kekayaan bersih saya 6 bulan terakhir" →
{ "intent": "asset_trend_query", "aggregation": "monthly", "requires_trend": true, "requires_account_breakdown": true }

"budget makan bulan ini sudah terpakai berapa?" →
{ "intent": "budget_query", "filters": { "categories": ["Makanan"] }, "requires_budget_data": true }
